<chapter id="standard_tasks">
    <title>Standard Gradle tasks</title>
    <para>There are a number of tasks included in the Gradle distribution. These are listed below.
    </para>
    <table>
        <title>Standard tasks</title>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <td>Task class</td>
                <td>Description</td>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tr>
